---
// CTA Section — Homepage
// Job: Letzter Impuls zur Conversion. Einladend, nicht drängend.
// Background: default (#0A0A0A) — kein farbiger Banner.
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-section relative overflow-hidden" aria-label="Termin buchen">
  <!-- Subtle radial glow — right side -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 right-[10%] -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(76, 175, 130, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%)"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-8 relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <h2>Klingt nach dem, was du suchst?</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-xl">
          Lass uns kennenlernen, über dein Marktplatzpotenzial sprechen und herausfinden, ob es passt.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a
            href="/kontakt"
            class="inline-block bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-background font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-button tracking-[0.01em] leading-none transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            Lern uns kennen
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
